<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Payment Processing</strong></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">Misr Travel requires a 25% deposit to confirm all bookings throughout the year except the periods the Christmas and New Year,&nbsp;Misr Travel&nbsp;requires a 50% deposit. Packages and vacations which include International flights will require the full flight cost and deposit (25% or 50%) <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="due to" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: because of, for" data-pwa-id="pwa-8D2A71F6DBCC8048F6BA9DAC9FE81DE0" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_3_1768" data-pwa-suggestions="because of~for">due to</pwa> the regulations of the Airlines.&nbsp;<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="Deposits can be made by bank wire transfer" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-FB3E6BD1475ABFE2D0725DF28921C8D1" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="Bank wire transfer can make deposits">Deposits can be made by bank wire transfer</pwa> or by credit card (Visa or MasterCard).</span></li>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">&nbsp;Full payment is due 4 weeks before the tour departure.</span></li>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="If paying by credit card, according to our bank regulations, the following documents are required" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-95E56F702E5DCC53AE98BC0DA78AF272" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="It requires if paying by credit card~They require if paying by credit card~I require if paying by credit card~I requires if paying by credit card~It require if paying by credit card~Something requires if paying by credit card~They requires if paying by credit card">If paying by credit card, according to our bank regulations, the following documents are required</pwa> to enable our accountant to charge your credit card for the agreed-upon services. These documents should <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="be faxed" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-23E35D1BE8F4C68C4EAEE306C9F1E02A" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">be faxed</pwa> or emailed to Misr Travel&nbsp;or given to our representative upon your arrival at the airport. Otherwise, we <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="will not be able to" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: cannot" data-pwa-id="pwa-D06E7BE8A10E3252FD7391935A47DDC5" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_1575" data-pwa-suggestions="cannot">will not be able to</pwa> proceed with completing your request.<br>
	• A copy of your passport.<br>
	• A copy of both sides of your credit card with your signature.<br>
	• A signed authorization letter to Misr Travel Egypt allowing the withdrawal of the required amount from your credit card. The signature must match&nbsp;that appearing on your credit card and passport.</span></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Payment by Bank Transfer &amp; Our Bank Account Details</strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Claims And Refunds:</strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">If you have any complaints while you are in Egypt, please notify Misr Travel Egypt&nbsp;immediately because most problems can<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word=" ." data-pwa-hint="The punctuation mark '.' may require a space after it, not before. Consider moving the space." data-pwa-id="pwa-FB09AB55D5107ACF380EDCDEDEAEEA30" data-pwa-rule-id="WHITESPACE" data-pwa-suggestions=". ">&nbsp;</pwa><pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word=" ." data-pwa-hint="The punctuation mark '.' may require a space after it, not before. Consider moving the space." data-pwa-id="pwa-FB09AB55D5107ACF380EDCDEDEAEEA30" data-pwa-rule-id="WHITESPACE" data-pwa-suggestions=". ">.</pwa>be solved quickly.&nbsp;A refund will normally <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="be made" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-E80DF8FFD5337600FF3459B421CE35FC" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">be made</pwa> to the same account and using the same method used for the original payment. No refunds are possible in the event of a no-show for an existing reservation. <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="Refunds are not made" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-E02CD401BD630EF7C041763B8B8AE232" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="It does not make refunds~I do not make refunds~They do not make refunds~It do not make refunds~Something does not make refunds~I does not make refunds">Refunds are not made</pwa> for any missed services, except for verifiable circumstances.&nbsp;For <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="claims to be considered" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-3C846197D3DD0060820922E8C4CE539D" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="us to consider claims~it to consider claims~something to consider claims~I to consider claims~someone to consider claims~they to consider claims">claims to be considered</pwa>, they must <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="be received" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-4569975F86D2B43F78375B372D9DC9C0" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">be received</pwa> in writing within 30 days of the termination of the program and <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="be accompanied" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-285CD62D68D53A1A11535A7387083BEA" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">be accompanied</pwa> by supporting documentation from the Operating Company verifying the claim. <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="Any adjustment considered will be based" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-476046E4CB48546897B2217D4611E95D" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I will base any adjustment considered~They will base any adjustment considered~It will base any adjustment considered">Any adjustment considered will be based</pwa> on the actual price of the services. <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="Adjustments will not be made" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-638C7EF1A94772C4B2EBDC404248C122" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I will not make adjustments~It will not make adjustments~They will not make adjustments">Adjustments will not be made</pwa> for unused sightseeing trips or meals. Misr Travel Tours will not accept any liability for any claims <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="that " data-pwa-hint="The word 'that' can often be omitted here" data-pwa-id="pwa-4A9546FA00702AB51BD6F9BEFECA7DCD" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_2834" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)">that&nbsp;</pwa><pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="are not received" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-31A2D67B84F188D67C000487EFEEDB13" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">are not received</pwa> within 30 days of the termination of your travel program. <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="All claims for days missed while travelling should be made" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-7B9E1247CFC5E60FED005282A5EF651F" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I should make all claims for days missed~It should make all claims for days missed~They should make all claims for days missed~Someone should make all claims for days missed">All claims for days missed while traveling should be made</pwa> in writing within 30 days of the termination of the program</span><br>
<span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Accommodation:</strong><br>
Unless otherwise stated, <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="prices are based" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-DA3E87B0655A8D30E542E29DDBDBD30D" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I base prices~they base prices~it bases prices~it base prices~something base prices~us base prices~us bases prices~I bases prices~someone bases prices~someone base prices">prices are based</pwa> on two persons sharing a room (twin sharing). Rooms for single occupants are available with an additional&nbsp;<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word="supplementary" data-pwa-hint="Possible missing determiner" data-pwa-id="pwa-0AF8919752345C59FD2B3C7037843293" data-pwa-rule-id="DET_CG_2" data-pwa-suggestions="a supplementary~the supplementary">supplementary</pwa> rate. Hotels and lodges <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="are named" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-2D614D23234A6FA80FE80139B51F1563" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">are named</pwa> as <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="an indication" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: a sign" data-pwa-id="pwa-43864E7A3C6965E603B05DC41DA453F0" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_2062" data-pwa-suggestions="a sign">an indication</pwa> of quality and <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="rooms may be reserved" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-81829D024E9347C9F22C3F3C2CF2E172" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="they may reserve rooms~it may reserve rooms~I may reserve rooms">rooms may be reserved</pwa> at an establishment of similar quality. Published prices are inclusive of tariffs and other costs at the time of printing and are subject to change without notice.<br>
<strong>Flights:</strong><br>
<strong>Domestic Flights:</strong><br>
The programs quote the average price of flights with approximate timings. Requests for specific flight times or changes to previously booked reservations may <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="result in" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: cause" data-pwa-id="pwa-7084BC053FC752746E04A52D6A8C9559" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_1103" data-pwa-suggestions="cause">result in</pwa> changes to the total price of the package.<br>
<br>
<strong>International Flights:</strong><br>
Misr Travel can assist you with international flights if needed. However, from our experience, international flights are best issued from the&nbsp;<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word="point" data-pwa-hint="Possible missing determiner" data-pwa-id="pwa-B6390F70ED6A110F1234D81F504B4C7A" data-pwa-rule-id="DET_CG_2" data-pwa-suggestions="a point~the point">point</pwa> of departure where the client has access to a wider range of price options and availability. The only way to pay for the international flights booked by Misr Travel is with a&nbsp;<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word="bank" data-pwa-hint="Possible missing determiner" data-pwa-id="pwa-F4A0818B6BBCE35A0D15703768CBF5F7" data-pwa-rule-id="DET_CG_2" data-pwa-suggestions="a bank~the bank">bank</pwa> transfer to Misr Travel&nbsp;Egypt Account.<br>
<br>
<strong>Responsibility:</strong><br>
The Company acts only as an agent for the participants <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="in regard to" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: regarding" data-pwa-id="pwa-2A1A7F7D94FA8B967C6913B861BB0B51" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_727" data-pwa-suggestions="regarding">in regard to</pwa> travel, whether by railroad, boat, aircraft, or any other mode of transport, and assume no liability for injury, illness, damage, loss, accident, delay, or irregularity to person or property resulting directly or indirectly from any of the following causes: weather, acts of God, force major, acts of government or other authorities, wars, civil disturbances, labor disputes, riots, theft, mechanical breakdowns, quarantines or acts of default, delays, cancellations or changes made by any hotel, carrier, or restaurant. <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="No responsibility is accepted" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-D4DED8478EDE7D9169D15B9A0B0202DA" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I accept no responsibility~They accept no responsibility~It accepts no responsibility~I accepts no responsibility~It accept no responsibility">No responsibility is accepted</pwa> for any additional expenses.<br>
<br>
<strong>Children Policy:</strong><br>
<em>• <strong><span style="color:#000000;">Policy 1: for packages, Nile cruises, and hotels</span></strong></em><br>
Under 2 years old: free<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word=" of charge" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by removing this" data-pwa-id="pwa-9AB2973613E879471DB659C00949267F" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_462" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)">&nbsp;of charge</pwa><br>
Under 6 years old: 25% of total tour cost for an individual<br>
Under 12 years old: 50% of total tour cost for an individual<br>
<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="All children 12 or older are considered" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-5BCEF07E192D20ED5DDFC9DF32D167CE" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I consider all children 12 or older~They consider all children 12 or older~It considers all children 12 or older~I considers all children 12 or older~Us consider all children 12 or older~It consider all children 12 or older">All children 12 or older are considered</pwa> adults.<br>
If your tour package includes flights, an extra supplement for your child may apply.<br>
<br>
<em>•<strong><span style="color:#000000;"> Policy 2: for sightseeing tours &amp; shore excursions</span></strong></em><br>
Under 6 years old: free<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word=" of charge" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by removing this" data-pwa-id="pwa-F6D0ED11A0A77E24282F9EC81DB5A11A" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_462" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)">&nbsp;of charge</pwa><br>
Under 12 years old: 50% of total tour cost for an individual<br>
<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="All children 12 or older are considered" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-631F35CA97D7F11FE1C2C5BCE1E2E855" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I consider all children 12 or older~They consider all children 12 or older~It considers all children 12 or older~I considers all children 12 or older~Us consider all children 12 or older~It consider all children 12 or older">All children 12 or older are considered</pwa> adults.<br>
If your sightseeing tours include domestic flights&nbsp;or ferry boats, an extra supplement for your child may apply.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Tipping:</strong><br>
Tipping is (discretionary<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word=" )" data-pwa-hint="The punctuation mark ')' may not require a space before it. Consider removing the space." data-pwa-id="pwa-04D4E13D66434797700798AEA384BAB0" data-pwa-rule-id="WHITESPACE" data-pwa-suggestions=")">&nbsp;)</pwa> to tour directors, drivers or local guides and express for your satisfaction with the services extended by them. <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="This is&nbsp;always appreciated" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-F6DDC93405403662CF0F411E9210E962" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="I always appreciate this~They always appreciate this">This is&nbsp;always appreciated</pwa> but <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="at the same time " data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by removing this" data-pwa-id="pwa-FD0B435072DA671893F8EB551BD1ACD8" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_1119" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)">at the same time&nbsp;</pwa><pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="spelling" data-pwa-dictionary-word="it,s" data-pwa-hint="Unknown word: it,s" data-pwa-id="pwa-36E43B8353F476BC92CD60D937EB2967" data-pwa-rule-id="SIMPLE_SPELLING" data-pwa-suggestions="it's~its">it,s</pwa> not obligatory.<br>
<br>
<strong>Acceptance of the agreement:</strong><br>
The contract <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="constituted" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: made up" data-pwa-id="pwa-B5F4C89B7CC9D7221B4EBAFA699B8BFA" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_2032" data-pwa-suggestions="made up">constituted</pwa> by the company's acceptance of the client's <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word="booking" data-pwa-hint="Incorrect verb after 's'" data-pwa-id="pwa-208AC5B74B18994F7D8BCB98294D2D5E" data-pwa-rule-id="PROG" data-pwa-suggestions="book~books">booking</pwa>, subject to these booking conditions, shall <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="constitute" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: make up" data-pwa-id="pwa-E4917DBE39502D1FB8CDEC1EC63A845C" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_2032" data-pwa-suggestions="make up">constitute</pwa> the entire agreement between the Client and the Company. The payment of a deposit or final payment by bank transfer or credit card <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="indicates" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: shows" data-pwa-id="pwa-F9A66DD65D25E87E9DC00BE786951811" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_2061" data-pwa-suggestions="shows">indicates</pwa> that tour participants have read and accepted all terms and conditions and agree to abide by them.</span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Misr Travel Vouchers</strong></span></p>

<ol>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">You will receive a personalized Misr Travel Voucher for your tour or service booked.</span></li>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">must provide the original, authentic Misr Travel Voucher&nbsp;to the <strong>&nbsp;</strong><pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="spelling" data-pwa-dictionary-word="Youappropriate" data-pwa-hint="Unknown word: Youappropriate" data-pwa-id="pwa-6F43A71A73A925B13377174542EF2952" data-pwa-rule-id="SIMPLE_SPELLING" data-pwa-suggestions="appropriate">You</pwa><pwa class="pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="" data-pwa-dictionary-word="appropriate " data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by removing this" data-pwa-id="pwa-A61C021F728D07670DBF00E8D004FB3D" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_1388" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)"><pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="spelling" data-pwa-dictionary-word="Youappropriate" data-pwa-hint="Unknown word: Youappropriate" data-pwa-id="pwa-6F43A71A73A925B13377174542EF2952" data-pwa-rule-id="SIMPLE_SPELLING" data-pwa-suggestions="appropriate">appropriate</pwa>&nbsp;</pwa>service provider <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="in order " data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by removing this" data-pwa-id="pwa-5FF30BB498217D890F1003D2E190DA36" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_640" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)">in order&nbsp;</pwa>to redeem your tour or package. Your reservation cannot <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="be honoured" data-pwa-hint="Passive verbs make your writing less direct. Try to use an active verb instead." data-pwa-id="pwa-7EF02B1A9AD1FA563752AB444D0A8552" data-pwa-rule-id="null" data-pwa-suggestions="">be honored</pwa> or redeemed without presenting a valid Misr Travel Voucher.</span></li>
</ol>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Passports, Visas &amp; Insurance</strong></span></p>

<ol>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">It is the responsibility of all passengers, regardless of nationality and destination, to check with the consulate of the country they are visiting for current entry requirements.</span></li>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">As visa and health requirements are subject to change without notice, we recommend that you verify health and visa requirements with the <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="appropriate " data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by removing this" data-pwa-id="pwa-7740DB92B94E15FDF0DD9210CB239FFE" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_1388" data-pwa-suggestions="(omit)">appropriate&nbsp;</pwa>consulate <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="prior to" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: before" data-pwa-id="pwa-A744375EB091F3A9EB587374FA0E0A4F" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_3065" data-pwa-suggestions="before">prior to</pwa> departure.</span></li>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">We strongly recommend that you purchase a comprehensive Travel Insurance Policy <pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="style" data-pwa-dictionary-word="prior to" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: before" data-pwa-id="pwa-E1165DC070B39E479D191452B758D429" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_3065" data-pwa-suggestions="before">prior to</pwa> departure. If you cancel your trip or significantly alter travel dates, many policies will reimburse the cost of cancellation fees and related expenses</span></li>
</ol>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Restrictions on Use</strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You agree that you will not, and will not assist or enable others to:</span></p>

<ol style="list-style-type:lower-roman;">
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">create a conflict of interest, such as trading reviews with other business owners or writing or soliciting reviews<pwa class="pwa-mark pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="grammar" data-pwa-dictionary-word=";" data-pwa-hint="The punctuation mark ';' may require a space after it. Consider adding the space." data-pwa-id="pwa-4C4C1A7A48B63FBC2A52D392C63BAF2C" data-pwa-rule-id="WHITESPACE" data-pwa-suggestions="; ">;&nbsp;</pwa><pwa class="pwa-mark-done" data-pwa-category="" data-pwa-dictionary-word="in a manner that may" data-pwa-hint="Readability may be enhanced by using: to" data-pwa-id="pwa-1EA857D0A6E8CFF413B4A48506E383B0" data-pwa-rule-id="READABILITY_1811" data-pwa-suggestions="to">in a manner that may use</pwa>&nbsp;the site </span></li>
	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif;">use the site to violate any third-party right, including any breach of confidence, copyright, trademark, patent, trade secret, moral right, privacy right, right of publicity, or any other intellectual property or proprietary right;<span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878083042_05190420667118345" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878083025_1728434813070685" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878082069_6487941527417584" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878082061_010608952542166206" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878077029_8333738976306966" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878077023_539037075998227" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878076077_2007336875861787" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878076058_8172388793398033" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878074046_23996966430518563" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878074039_5550032491365093" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878070656_9241975742687931" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span><span class="rangySelectionBoundary" id="selectionBoundary_1546878070651_9406146550231174" style="line-height: 0; display: none;">﻿</span></span></li>
